\n\n===Serial films===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- style=\"background:#b0c4de;\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Production studio\n! Notes\n! Chapters\n|-\n| 1941\n| ''[[Adventures of Captain Marvel]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Republic Pictures]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|Published at that time by [[Fawcett Comics]]\n| align=\"center\"|12\n|-\n| 1942\n| ''[[Spy Smasher (serial)|Spy Smasher]]''\n| align=\"center\"|12\n|-\n| 1943\n| ''[[Batman (serial)|Batman]]''\n| rowspan=\"8\"|[[Columbia Pictures]]\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| 1946\n| ''[[Hop Harrigan (serial)|Hop Harrigan]]''\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| 1947\n| ''[[The Vigilante]]''\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|1948\n| ''[[Superman (serial)|Superman]]''\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| ''[[Congo Bill (serial)|Congo Bill]]''\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| 1949\n| ''[[Batman and Robin (serial)|Batman and Robin]]''\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| 1950\n| ''[[Atom Man vs. Superman]]''\n|\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|-\n| 1952\n| ''[[The Miraculous Blackhawk: Freedom's Champion]]''\n| Published at that time by [[Quality Comics]]\n| align=\"center\"|15\n|}\n\n===From DC imprints===\n;Vertigo\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Production studio\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[V for Vendetta (film)|V for Vendetta]]''\n| Warner Bros./[[Virtual Studios]]/[[Silver Pictures]]/[[The Wachowskis|Anarchos Productions]]/[[Medienboard Berlin-Brandenburg]]/F\u00fcnfte Babelsberg Film GmbH\n| Based on the [[V for Vendetta|graphic novel]] by [[Alan Moore]] and [[David Lloyd (comics)|David Lloyd]]\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[The Losers (film)|The Losers]]''\n| Warner Bros./DC Comics/[[Dark Castle Entertainment]]\n| Based on the [[The Losers (Vertigo)|series]] by [[Andy Diggle]] and [[Jock (comics)|Jock]]\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[The Kitchen (2019 film)|The Kitchen]]''\n| Warner Bros./New Line Cinema/DC Vertigo/Bron Creative/Michael De Luca Productions\n| Based on the original miniseries by Ollie Masters and Ming Doyle\n|}\