am|title=Shazam! (2019)|work=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]]|accessdate=February 21, 2020}}</ref>\n| 70 (53 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/shazam!|title=Shazam! reviews|work=[[Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=April 5, 2019}}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|A}}<ref name=\"DCcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Joker''\n| 68% (548 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/joker_2019|title=Joker (2019)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]]|accessdate=February 20, 2020}}</ref>\n| 59 (58 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/joker|title=Joker reviews|work=[[Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=November 19, 2019}}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B+}}<ref name=\"DCcs\" />\n|-\n| ''Birds of Prey''\n| 78% (386 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/birds_of_prey_2020|title=Birds of Prey (2020)|website=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango (company)|Fandango]]|accessdate=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n| 60 (59 reviews)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/birds-of-prey-and-the-fantabulous-emancipation-of-one-harley-quinn|title=Birds of Prey reviews|work=[[Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=February 14, 2020}}</ref>\n| {{sort grade|B+}}<ref name=\"DCcs\" />\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align: left;\"| <small>'''List indicator(s)'''\n* A dark grey cell indicates information is not available for the film.</small>\n|}\n\n===From DC imprints===\n;Vertigo\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" width=99% border=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|- style=\"background:#b0c4de;\"\n! Title\n! Distributor(s)\n! Release date\n! Rotten Tomatoes\n! Metacritic\n! CinemaScore<ref name=\"DCcs\" />\n! Budget <br />(million)\n! Box Office\n|-\n| ''V for Vendetta''\n| rowspan=\"3\"| Warner Bros.\n| March 17, 2006\n| 73% (248 reviews)<ref>{{cite web |title= V for Vendetta (2006) |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/